Prey","original_language":"en"},{"id":467455,"adult":false,"title":"Strike Zone","video":false,"overview":"In Sofia, Bulgaria, Lt. Col. John Hart, Lt. Rick Burns and an elite team of Navy SEALS are on a mission to stop the transfer of missile guidance technology to a Mid-Eastern country. The system's computer control is hidden in a fake archaeological site - the Lost City of Rajkumar.","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":0.3006,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/7Qj0TulVhx2YVzyTeIBX3IYRQon.jpg","release_date":"2000-05-17","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":"/6F1XTyeEnYPxtoWvvqVyPJy1ugh.jpg","original_title":"Strike Zone","original_language":"en"},{"id":9080,"adult":false,"title":"Spies Like Us","video":false,"overview":"Two bumbling government employees think they are U.S. spies, only to discover that they are actually decoys for nuclear war.","genre_ids":[35,12],"popularity":2.4943,"vote_count":686,"poster_path":"/s0Sx8nd9Irq0aCPbsN78s0DYVlG.jpg","release_date":"1985-12-06","vote_average":6.182,"backdrop_path":"/9RJGN6CaCFOzs9H1yie2aPxLUoX.jpg","original_title":"Spies Like Us","original_language":"en"},{"id":9273,"adult":false,"title":"Ace Ventura: When Nature Calls","video":false,"overview":"Summoned from an ashram in Tibet, Ace finds himself on a perilous journey into the jungles of Africa to find Shikaka, the missing sacred animal of the friendly Wachati tribe. He must accomplish this before the wedding of the Wachati's Princess to the prince of the warrior Wachootoos. If Ace fails, the result will be a vicious tribal war.","genre_ids":[80,35,12],"popularity":2.99,"vote_count":4449,"poster_path":"/wcinCf1ov2D6M3P7BBZkzQFOiIb.jpg","release_date":"1995-11-10","vote_average":6.32,"backdrop_path":"/h5Y9T4OoFpMrONhVBZvN2X2DfAB.jpg","original_title":"Ace Ventura: When Nature Calls","original_language":"en"},{"id":8961,"adult":false,"title":"Bad Boys II","video":false,"overview":"Detectives Marcus Burnett and Mike Lowrey of the Miami Narcotics Task Force are tasked with stopping the flow of the drug Ecstasy into Miami. They track the drugs to the whacked-out Cuban drug lord Johnny Tapia, who is also involved in a bloody war with Russian and Haitian mobsters. If that isn't bad enough, there's tension between the two detectives when Marcus discovers that playboy Mike is secretly romancing Marcus’ sister, Syd.","genre_ids":[28,80,35],"popularity":5.5211,"vote_count":5825,"poster_path":"/yCvB5fG5aEPqa1St7ihY6KEAsHD.jpg","release_date":"2003-07-18","vote_average":6.656,"backdrop_path":"/gxSVZCUlDd8upT1G2wdrUdz2hxG.jpg","original_title":"Bad Boys II","original_language":"en"},{"id":8975,"adult":false,"title":"The Marine","video":false,"overview":"A group of diamond thieves on the run kidnap the wife of a recently discharged marine who goes on a chase through the South Carolinian wilderness to retrieve her.","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":1.7319,"vote_count":806,"poster_path":"/pONyvBJwHNg5CWu7mtsv4qaq75C.jpg","release_date":"2006-10-13","vote_average":5.973,"backdrop_path":"/aldhT4Y0t6y2TkDC6wYiowj5wRL.jpg","original_title":"The Marine","original_language":"en"},{"id":8987,"adult":false,"title":"The River Wild","video":false,"overview":"Gail and Tom Hartman are struggling to stay together and decide to take a white-water rafting holiday adventure in Montana for their son Roarke's 10th birthday, only to meet up with a pair of mysterious men whose desperation grows, turning their vacation into a nightmare.","genre_ids":[12,53,18],"popularity":1.4529,"vote_count":939,"poster_path":"/wVgQ2T63ThjIsY4R0qoHXjyllql.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-30","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/yIWtX0ulnAUrbd12F9foRzHaT1M.jpg","original_title":"The River Wild","original_language":"en"},{"id":8843,"adult":false,"title":"The Cell","video":false,"overview":"A psychotherapist journeys inside a comatose serial killer in the hopes of saving his latest victim.","genre_ids":[27,878,53],"popularity":3.5761,"vote_count":1667,"poster_path":"/kfYVxvDDAJoFq2knHUzAZP09pAc.jpg","re