re,\" an inventive ant named Flik hires a troupe of warrior bugs to defend his bustling colony from a horde of freeloading grasshoppers led by the evil-minded Hopper.","genre_ids":[10751,16,12,35],"popularity":8.5765,"vote_count":9609,"poster_path":"/Ah3J9OJVc2CNCuH2zMydXy9fmIC.jpg","release_date":"1998-11-25","vote_average":6.973,"backdrop_path":"/hwwFyowfcbLRVmRBOkvnABBNIOs.jpg","original_title":"A Bug's Life","original_language":"en"},{"id":9488,"adult":false,"title":"Spy Kids 2: The Island of Lost Dreams","video":false,"overview":"Exploring the further adventures of Carmen and Juni Cortez, who have now joined the family spy business as Level 2 OSS agents. Their new mission is to save the world from a mad scientist living on a volcanic island populated by an imaginative menagerie of creatures. On this bizarre island, none of the Cortez's gadgets work and they must rely on their wits--and each other--to survive and save the day.","genre_ids":[10751,28,12,35,878],"popularity":3.6028,"vote_count":2315,"poster_path":"/z8pfWCk6SlxxDLXXQdUHdxF5dwJ.jpg","release_date":"2002-08-07","vote_average":5.653,"backdrop_path":"/5rKa5UKXnTdLsgY0mJbjAEQX3gB.jpg","original_title":"Spy Kids 2: The Island of Lost Dreams","original_language":"en"},{"id":9509,"adult":false,"title":"Man on Fire","video":false,"overview":"Jaded ex-CIA operative John Creasy reluctantly accepts a job as the bodyguard for a 10-year-old girl in Mexico City. They clash at first, but eventually bond, and when she's kidnapped he's consumed by fury and will stop at nothing to save her life.","genre_ids":[28,18,53],"popularity":6.7485,"vote_count":5531,"poster_path":"/grCGLCcTHv9TChibzOwzUpykcjB.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-23","vote_average":7.457,"backdrop_path":"/6c7j7MQCczzNVvcrNEiXbs8Kt2p.jpg","original_title":"Man on Fire","original_language":"en"},{"id":9370,"adult":false,"title":"The Spy","video":false,"overview":"The British Admiralty is worried: several cargo ships carrying troops have mysteriously jumped off Gibraltar. The Admiralty calls in the Intelligence Service to find out the cause of the destruction before new units arrive. Lieutenant Jackson, of the Marine Infantry Regiment stationed in Gibraltar, spends all his duty time in Tangier, where he is attracted by his love of poker and a beautiful dancer, Lola. Despite the objurgations of his general and the tender friendship of Cathie, his general's daughter, he can't stop playing and loses a very large sum one evening.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":0.3755,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/5DSsX4DQSL3bMbrVe5vFWfZMEKh.jpg","release_date":"1964-02-27","vote_average":3,"backdrop_path":"/tYwb1ub8qKxplnB8140WzThHXWV.jpg","original_title":"Gibraltar","original_language":"fr"},{"id":9320,"adult":false,"title":"The Avengers","video":false,"overview":"British Ministry agent John Steed, under direction from \"Mother\", investigates a diabolical plot by arch-villain Sir August de Wynter to rule the world with his weather control machine. Steed investigates the beautiful Doctor Mrs. Emma Peel, the only suspect, but simultaneously falls for her and joins forces with her to combat Sir August.","genre_ids":[28,12,53,878,35],"popularity":2.0671,"vote_count":762,"poster_path":"/1p5thyQ4pCy876HpdvFARqJ62N9.jpg","release_date":"1998-08-13","vote_average":4.442,"backdrop_path":"/nMjfRk5SBNuxT01f5FYO5rJLwnI.jpg","original_title":"The Avengers","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt1375666","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":"","wikidata_id":"Q25188","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/inception","mydramalist_id":"195180","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/inception"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":"","instagram":null},"gdvg_id":100128,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AE","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1